text: Gonzalo Domínguez (born 26 August 1925) was a Chilean alpine skier. He competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Chilean male alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Chile Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
